title: pyRomanNumerals2Integer
content:
# Convert Roman Numerals To Integer
# Mike Kerry - December 2020, August 2023 - acclivity2@gmail.com

def convert_roman_to_int(s):
    roman = {'I': 1, 'V': 5, 'X': 10, 'L': 50, 'C': 100, 'D': 500, 'M': 1000}
    result, prev = 0, 0
    for c in s.upper():         # iterate through Roman Numeral string
        v = roman[c]            # Get value of current character
        if v > prev:            # is the current letter value greater than the previous? ...
            result -= 2*prev    # ... yes, e.g. IX we had already added 1 but should have deducted 1
        result += v             # add value of this letter to result
        prev = v                # remember value of latest letter
    return result


tests = ["MMDCXL", "MCCCXLIX", "CDXXXVIII"]

for t in tests:
    ps = convert_roman_to_int(t)
    print(t, " = ", ps)


# Results:-
# MMDCXL  =  2640
# MCCCXLIX  =  1349
# CDXXXVIII  =  438

title: vimrc
content:
" BASIC OPTS ---------------------------- {{{

set shell=/bin/bash

" Disable VI compat
set nocompatible


" color scheme
colorscheme torte
" Detect file types
filetype on

" Plugins Enable
filetype plugin on

" Indents
filetype indent on

" Syntax highlighting
syntax on

" Line numbers
set number
set relativenumber

" Hilight cursor Horizontally & Vertically
set cursorline
set cursorcolumn

set shiftwidth=2
set tabstop=2
set softtabstop=2
set expandtab

" Don't save backups
set nobackup

" Do not let cursor scroll below or above N lines
set scrolloff=15

set nowrap

" incremental Search
set incsearch

set ignorecase

set smartcase

" Show partial commands
set showcmd

" Show current mode
set showmode

" Show matching words
set showmatch

" Highlight matches when searching
set hlsearch

" Cmd history
set history=1000

" Wildmenu Tab completion
"set wildmenu

set wildmode=list:longest

" Never open these in VIM
set wildignore=*.docx,*.jpg,*.png,*.gif,*.pdf,*.pyc,*.exe,*.flv,*.img,*.xlsx,*.mp3


" runtimepath & packpath -- mostly for windows
set runtimepath^="~/.vim/plugged"
let &packpath = &runtimepath

" vim-plug logs
let g:plug_log_on = 1
" }}}




" PLUGINS ------------------------------- {{{

" using vim-plug
call plug#begin('~/.vim/plugged')
  Plug 'preservim/nerdtree'
  Plug 'ap/vim-css-color' "CSS Color Preview
  Plug 'tpope/vim-commentary'
  Plug 'mattn/emmet-vim'
  Plug 'nathanaelkane/vim-indent-guides'
  Plug 'romainl/vim-cool'
  Plug 'ryanoasis/vim-devicons'
call plug#end()
" }}} 


" MAPPINGS ------------------------------ {{{

" }}}


" VIMSCRIPT ----------------------------- {{{

" This will enable code folding.
" User the marker method of folding.
" zO = open single, zc = close fold
" zR = open all folds, zM = close all folds
augroup filetype_vim
	autocmd!
	autocmd FileType vim setlocal foldmethod=marker
augroup END


if has("autocmd")
  " HTML indentation
  autocmd FileType html setlocal tabstop=2 shiftwidth=2 expandtab
  autocmd FileType css setlocal ts=2 sts=2 sw=2 expandtab
  autocmd FileType javascript setlocal ts=2 sts=2 sw=2 expandtab

  autocmd FileType make setlocal ts=8 sts=8 sw=8 noexpandtab
  autocmd FileType php setlocal ts=4 sts=4 sw=4 expandtab
endif
" Enable undo
if version >= 703
	set undodir=~/.vim/backup
	set undofile
	set undoreload=10000
endif

" Split window using :split or :vsplit
" Display cursorline and cursorcolumn ONLY in active window
augroup cursor_off
	autocmd!
	autocmd WinLeave * set nocursorline nocursorcolumn
	autocmd WinEnter * set cursorline cursorcolumn
augroup END

" Some GUI Options
if has('gui_running')

	set background=dark

	colorscheme molokai

	" Font syntax: <font_name>\ <weight>\ <size>
	set guifont=Monospace\ Regular\ 12

	" hide toolbar
	set guioptions-=T

	" Hide Left-side scroll bars
	set guioptions-=L
	set guioptions-=r

	" Hide menu
	set guioptions-=m

	" Hide bottom scroll
	set guioptions-=b

	" Set a keymap for F4 to toggle
	" <Bar> is | character
	nnoremap <F4> :if &guioptions=~#'mTr'<Bar>

function JKescape(key) abort
  if a:key ==# 'j'
    let b:esc_j_lasttime = reltimefloat(reltime())
    return a:key
  endif
  let l:timediff = reltimefloat(reltime()) - get(b:, 'esc_j_lasttime')
  let b:esc_j_lasttime = 0.0
  return l:timediff <= 0.1 && l:timediff > 0.001 ? "\b\e" : a:key
endfunction

content:
local replicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
local serverScriptService = game:GetService("ServerScriptService")
local players = game:GetService("Players")

--{{SETTINGS}}
local config = require(script.Settings)

DS_NAME = config.DS_NAME
DEFAULT_DATA = config.DEFAULT_DATA

AUTOSAVE_TIME = config.AUTOSAVE_TIME --in seconds.
BLACKLIST = config.BLACKLIST

--{{SCRIPT}}
local namesService = require(game.ServerScriptService.Modules.NamesModule)
local DSS = game:GetService("DataStoreService")

local datastore = DSS:GetDataStore(DS_NAME)
local hotbarDatastore = DSS:GetDataStore(DS_NAME .. "_HOTBARSAVES2")
local questDatastore = DSS:GetDataStore(DS_NAME .. "_QUESTSAVES")
local itemDatastore = DSS:GetDataStore(DS_NAME .. "_ITEMSAVES")

local playerdatafolder = game:GetService("ServerStorage"):WaitForChild("PlayerData")
local players = game:GetService("Players")
local loadCharacter = require(script.LoadCharacter)
local hotbarSaves = require(script.HotbarSaves)
local questSaves = require(script.QuestSaves)
local itemSaves = require(script.InventorySaves)

local core = require(game.ServerScriptService.Modules.CoreModule)

function getDataKey(player)
	return "id-"..player.UserId
end

function generateDataTable(player)
	if not playerdatafolder:FindFirstChild(player.Name) then return end
	local datatable = {}
	for _,v in pairs(playerdatafolder[player.Name]:GetChildren()) do
		datatable[v.Name] = {v.Value, v.ClassName}
	end
	return datatable
end

function savePlayerData(player)
	if replicatedStorage.ClientStatus.PermaDeath.Value then return end
	local hotbar = hotbarSaves.getHotbar(player)
	local quests = questSaves.getSavedQuests(player)
	local items = itemSaves.getInventory(player)

	local key = getDataKey(player)
	local data = generateDataTable(player)

	datastore:SetAsync(key, data)
	if hotbar then hotbarDatastore:SetAsync(key, hotbar) end
	if quests then questDatastore:SetAsync(key, quests) end
	if items then itemDatastore:SetAsync(key, items) end
end

function loadPlayerData(player)
	local key = getDataKey(player)
	local data = datastore:GetAsync(key)

	local hotbardata = hotbarDatastore:GetAsync(key)
	local questdata = questDatastore:GetAsync(key)
	local itemdata = itemDatastore:GetAsync(key)
	return data, hotbardata, questdata, itemdata
end

local exp = require(game.ServerScriptService.Modules.EXPModule)

function playerAdded(player)
	for _,v in pairs(BLACKLIST) do
		if v == player.Name then
			player:Kick("BANNED")
		end
	end

	local savedData, savedHotbar, savedQuests, savedInventory

	local success, msg = pcall(function()
		savedData, savedHotbar, savedQuests, savedInventory = loadPlayerData(player)
	end)
	if success == false then
		player:Kick("Error loading savedata.")
	end

	local clientdata = Instance.new("Folder", player)
	clientdata.Name = "Data"

	local datafolder = Instance.new("Folder")
	datafolder.Name = player.Name
	datafolder.Parent = playerdatafolder

	do
		local value = Instance.new("IntValue")
		value.Name = "Nation"
		value.Parent = datafolder

		local hardcodes = require(script.Hardcodes)

		local function findUserNumber(username)
			for number, userTable in pairs(hardcodes) do
				for names,_ in userTable do
					if string.find(string.lower(names), string.lower(username)) then
						return number
					end
				end
			end

			return nil
		end

		local usernameToFind = player.Name
		local userNumber = findUserNumber(usernameToFind)

		if userNumber then
			value.Value = tonumber(userNumber)
		else
			value.Value = math.random(0, 3)
		end
	end

	for k,v in pairs(DEFAULT_DATA) do
		--v[1] is the value
		--v[2] is the value type
		local value
		if k ~= "Nation" then
			value = Instance.new(v[2])
			value.Value = v[1]
			value.Name = k
			value.Parent = datafolder
		end
		if k == "Age" then
			value.Value = math.random(10,17)
		elseif k == "ArmorType" then
			value.Value = "Starter"..math.random(0,2)
		elseif k == "HairColor" then
			value.Value = math.random(1,#game.ServerStorage.CharAppearance.HairTextures:GetChildren()-1)
		elseif k == "SkinTone" then
			value.Value = math.random(1,#game.ServerStorage.CharAppearance.SkinTones:GetChildren())
		elseif k == "ClothesVariant" then
			value.Value = math.random(1,2)
		elseif k == "CharName" then
			value.Value = namesService:getName(datafolder.Nation.Value)
		elseif k == "CharBrows" or k =="CharMouth" or k == "CharNose" or k =="CharEyes" then
			local folder = game.ServerStorage.CharAppearance[k]
			value.Value = folder:GetChildren()[math.random(1,#folder:GetChildren())].Name
		elseif k == "SpawnArea" then
			local Nations = {
				[0] = "Earth",
				[1] = "Fire",
				[2] = "Water",
				[3] = "Air",
				[906] = "Air",
			}
			value.Value = Nations[datafolder.Nation.Value].." Nation"
		elseif k == "ArmorType" then
			if datafolder.Nation.Value == 3 then
				value.Value = "Air Nomad Outfit"
			end
		end
	end

	local a, b = pcall(function()
		if savedData ~= nil and savedData ~= 0 then
			print("Loading savedata for "..player.Name)
			for _,v in pairs(datafolder:GetChildren()) do
				if savedData[v.Name] then
					v.Value = savedData[v.Name][1]
				end
			end
		else
			print("Creating savedata for "..player.Name)
			savePlayerData(player)
		end
	end)

	if a == false then
		player:Kick("Data loaded incorrectly")
	else
		local a = Instance.new("IntValue", clientdata)
		a.Name = "DATALOADED"
	end

	core.createReplicatedValue("AdvancedDodge", clientdata, datafolder.AdvancedDodge)
	core.createReplicatedValue("ReplicatedYuan", clientdata, datafolder.Yuan)
	core.createReplicatedValue("Nation", clientdata, datafolder.Nation)
	core.createReplicatedValue("SkillPoints", clientdata, datafolder.SkillPoints)
	core.createReplicatedValue("PowerStat", clientdata, datafolder.PowerStat)
	core.createReplicatedValue("ControlStat", clientdata, datafolder.ControlStat)
	core.createReplicatedValue("LavaBending", clientdata, datafolder.LavaBending)
	core.createReplicatedValue("MetalBending", clientdata, datafolder.MetalBending)
	core.createReplicatedValue("LightningBending", clientdata, datafolder.LightningBending)
	core.createReplicatedValue("CharName", clientdata, datafolder.CharName)
	core.createReplicatedValue("Hunger", clientdata, datafolder.Hunger)

	if datafolder.FirstJoined.Value then
		local fj = Instance.new("IntValue", clientdata)
		fj.Name = "FirstJoined"

		datafolder.FirstJoined.Value = false
	end

	local function characterAdded(char)
		loadCharacter(datafolder, player, char)
	end

	if savedHotbar then
		hotbarSaves.updateHotbar(player, savedHotbar)
	end
	if savedQuests then
		questSaves.updateQuests(player, savedQuests)
	end
	if savedInventory then
		itemSaves.updateInventory(player, savedInventory)
	end

	if player.Character then
		characterAdded(player.Character)
	end

	player.CharacterAdded:Connect(characterAdded)

	if datafolder.CompletedTutorial.Value == false then
		game.ReplicatedStorage.ClientStuff.TutorialGUI:Clone().Parent = player:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")
	end

	player:WaitForChild("Backpack").ChildRemoved:Connect(function(child)
		if child:IsA("Tool") and child.Parent ~= player.Character and not player:FindFirstChild("SafeToolRemove") then
			game.ReplicatedStorage.Events.InventoryActions:Fire(player, "remove", child.Name)
			datafolder.UtilTool.Value = ""
		end
	end)
end

function playerRemoving(player)	
	local character = workspace.Living:FindFirstChild(player.Name) or workspace:FindFirstChild(player.Name)
	if character then character:Destroy() end

	local datafolder = game.ServerStorage.PlayerData:FindFirstChild(player.Name)
	if player.Data:FindFirstChild("DATALOADED") then
		if datafolder and player:FindFirstChild("CombatTag") then
			datafolder.Yuan.Value = 0
			datafolder.LevelEXP.Value = math.clamp(datafolder.LevelEXP.Value-math.abs(datafolder.LevelEXP.Value) - 15, -50, math.huge)

			if replicatedStorage.ClientStatus.PermaDeath.Value then
				serverScriptService.MainScripts.Datastore.wipePlayerDataDind:Invoke(player)
			end
		end
		savePlayerData(player)

		if datafolder then
			datafolder:Destroy()
		end
		wait(1)
	end
end

if game.JobId ~= "" or game.ServerScriptService["_serversettings"].SaveInStudio.Value then
	game:BindToClose(function()
		for _,player in pairs(players:GetPlayers()) do
			if player then
				local tag = player:FindFirstChild("CombatTag")
				if tag then
					tag:Destroy()
				end

				player:Kick("Shutdown")
			end
		end

		wait(5)
	end)
end

local function wipePlayerData(player)
	if player then
		player:Kick()
		wait(5)
		local dataKey = getDataKey(player)

		-- Remove the player's data from the datastore
		local success, errorMsg = pcall(function()
			datastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
			hotbarDatastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
			questDatastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
			itemDatastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
		end)

		if not success then
			warn("Error while removing data:", errorMsg)
		else
			print("Player data wiped successfully.")
			-- Save the wiped state to the datastore immediately
			savePlayerData(player)
			playerAdded(player) -- Optionally, you might want to call playerAdded to reset the player's data
		end

		delay(5, function()
			local dataKey = getDataKey(player)

			-- Remove the player's data from the datastore
			local success, errorMsg = pcall(function()
				datastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
				hotbarDatastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
				questDatastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
				itemDatastore:RemoveAsync(dataKey)
			end)

			if not success then
				warn("Error while removing data:", errorMsg)
			else
				print("Player data wiped successfully.")
				-- Save the wiped state to the datastore immediately
				savePlayerData(player)
				playerAdded(player) -- Optionally, you might want to call playerAdded to reset the player's data
			end
		end)
	else
		warn("Player not found.")
	end
end

script.wipePlayerData.OnServerInvoke = function(player)
	if player then
		--wipePlayerData(player)
		return true
	else
		return false
	end
end

script.wipePlayerDataDind.OnInvoke = function(player)
	if player then
		wipePlayerData(player)
		return true
	else
		return false
	end
end

players.PlayerAdded:Connect(playerAdded)
players.PlayerRemoving:Connect(playerRemoving)

coroutine.resume(coroutine.create(function()
	while wait(AUTOSAVE_TIME) do
		for _,v in pairs(players:GetPlayers()) do
			savePlayerData(v)
		end
	end
end))

Logo Quiz! Badge Script
content:
--[[
	A quick script for Logo Quiz
	https://www.roblox.com/games/13333567382/Logo-Quiz

	This just gets all badges for you.
]]

local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local Workspace = game:GetService("Workspace")

local LocalPlayer = Players.LocalPlayer
local Character = LocalPlayer.Character or LocalPlayer.CharacterAdded:Wait()

for i,v in pairs(Workspace:GetDescendants()) do
	if v:IsA("TouchTransmitter") then
		if v.Parent.Name == v.Parent.Parent.Name and v.Parent:IsA("BasePart") and v.Parent.Parent:IsA("Model") and v.Parent.Parent:FindFirstChild("Parts") ~= nil then continue end -- Tool check

		firetouchinterest(Character.HumanoidRootPart, v.Parent, 1)
		firetouchinterest(Character.HumanoidRootPart, v.Parent, 0)
	end
end

#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
"""
Script que pide una ruta y una extension e imprime todos los archivos
hallados y el total encontrado
>>> python buscar_archivos.py <ruta> <extension>
"""
import os                            
import sys

hallados = 0

# verifico la cantidad de argumentos
if len(sys.argv) != 3:
	sys.exit("Error: Debe ejecutar 'python buscar_archivos.py <ruta> <extension>'")

# asigno los parámetros
ruta, extension = sys.argv[1:]

# verifico si existe la ruta
if not os.path.exists(ruta):
	sys.exit(f"No existe la ruta '{ruta}'")
	
'''
voy a buscar en forma recursiva dentro de la ruta con os.walk().
os.walk() trabaja con 3 iteradores simultáneamente:
a) El nombre de la carpeta actual
b) Una lista de carpetas dentro de la carpeta actual
c) una lista de archivos dentro de la carpeta actual
'''
for carpeta_actual, lista_carpetas, lista_archivos in os.walk(ruta):
	for archivo in lista_archivos:
		if archivo.endswith(extension):
			print(os.path.join(carpeta_actual, archivo))
			hallados += 1
			
			
if not hallados:
	print(f"No se hallaron archivos con extension '{extension}' en la ruta '{ruta}'")
else:
	print(f"\nTotal: {hallados}")

--Listener for the CC Todo Personalized

function mysplit (inputstr, sep)
        if sep == nil then
                sep = "%s"
        end
        local t={}
        for str in string.gmatch(inputstr, "([^"..sep.."]+)") do
                table.insert(t, str)
        end
        return t
end

local todo = {}

peripheral.find("modem", rednet.open)
local monitor = peripheral.find("monitor")

while true do
	monitor.clear()
	monitor.setCursorPos(1, 1)
	monitor.write("Todo List:")
	for id,task in pairs(todo) do
		monitor.setCursorPos(1,1+id)
		monitor.write("["..id.."] "..task)
	end
	id, message = rednet.receive()
	if id == 2 then
		if message == "End" then
			break
		else
			usertask = mysplit(message, ":")
			if usertask[2] == "Clear" then
				todo[usertask[1]] = nil
			else
				todo[usertask[1]] = usertask[2]
			end
		end
	else
		--do nothing
	end
end

function checkSpruceLog(info)
    success, data = info
    if success then
        if data.name == 'minecraft:spruce_logs' then
            return true
        end
    end
    return false
end

function mineUp()
    while checkSpruceLog(turtle.detectUp()) do
        turtle.digUp()
        turtle.up()
    end
end

function mineDown()
    while checkSpruceLog(turtle.detectDown()) do
        turtle.digDown()
        turtle.down()
    end
end

function mineSpruce()
    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    mineUp()
    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    mineDown()
    turtle.turnRight()
    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    mineUp()
    turtle.turnRight()
    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    mineDown()
end

mineSpruce()

local gui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
gui.Name = ""
for i=1,50 do
    gui.Name = gui.Name..tostring(math.random(1,9))
end
gui.ResetOnSpawn = false
gui.Parent = game.CoreGui

local textlabel = Instance.new("TextLabel")
textlabel.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(50,50,50)
textlabel.BorderColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255)
textlabel.Size = UDim2.new(.2,0,.4,0)
textlabel.Position = UDim2.new(.4,0,.3)
textlabel.TextScaled = true
textlabel.Active = true
textlabel.Draggable = true
textlabel.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255)
textlabel.Parent = gui
local mouse = game.Players.LocalPlayer:GetMouse()
mouse.Button1Down:Connect(function()
    local target = mouse.Target
    textlabel.Text = target:GetFullName()
end)
